Congratulations on getting ready to apply to college! Applying is the first step in starting your journey in higher education.

We're especially excited that you wish to apply to the Mount! Whether you're applying as an undergraduate, graduate, transfer or degree completion student, the process is simple and fast. Choose one of the application methods below to get started:
Please note, you are not required to reapply if you were previously enrolled at Mount Saint Mary College. If you wish to return to the college to complete your degree, please fill out our
Five things to have ready before you apply to the Mount:
Basic information about yourself and your family: email and physical addresses, phone numbers, and employers
Information about your current or past schools: Names, addresses, and guidance counselor information
What you want to study (Not sure yet? You can also select undeclared!)
Letters of reference, SAT/ACT scores, transcripts (either to upload with the application if you have them or as you receive these materials)
Excitement! This is a huge life step, so make sure you take a moment to enjoy it!
